{"tid":951002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋 人] 希望大家幫幫手，祝 冬至快樂","createTime":"2018-12-22T03:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T12:40:06.000Z","uid":116561,"like":51,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"31ff0dbf4837ab67fd2ef87de3142b1d751255fd","tid":951002,"uid":116561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:35:36.000Z","msg":"代友出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n《尋 人》<br />\n希望大家幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n本人爸爸 林廣源 先生 <br />\n年齡：58歲<br />\n國籍：中國籍男子 操流利廣東話 本土香港人<br />\n穿著：棗紅色長袖有領衫 深藍色長褲 紅色Nike 波鞋<br />\n報案編號：LMCRN18014410<br />\n<br />\n昨日21/12/2018（五）晚上七時（19:00）因與家人有小問題嘈交，而踏出家門（上水洲頭村） 至今22/12/2018（六）早上九時半（09:30）仍未回家。<br />\n<br />\n出門時 沒有攜帶 身份證、銀包、電話、車匙、八達通。所有物件均在家裡，只著咗兩件單薄嘅衫就出咗去。<br />\n<br />\n起初大家以為佢去搵鄰居傾計/去人屋企睇電視舒壓，因以往都係咁。結果食完飯晚上八時（20:00）去鄰居處尋找並詢問，而結果是沒有見過我爸爸。我哋都即刻意識到問題有幾嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n我同老公分別以 人行方式 及 車行方式係屋企附近以及山上都搵過。搵到凌晨十二點（00:00）左右，媽媽致電話太夜搵唔到，叫我哋返屋企休息下先。<br />\n<br />\n經過大家商量 決定報警，於是係凌晨一點九（01:45）報警求助。警察都好快咁嚟咗屋企錄口供，睇下周圍環境，亦做咗一輪快速搜索（睇下附近山崖邊，去周圍睇）。直至凌晨約四點（04:00）都係搵唔到。<br />\n<br />\n今日我哋將會到爸爸工作或者會去嘅地方搵下，如果大家有任何消息希望可以提供俾我地<br />\n或者幫手諗諗58歲嘅中年男士嬲會去邊<br />\n<br />\n爸爸並無長期病患 但膝頭同心臟都唔好，希望大家幫幫手，全家都好擔心<br />\n<br />\n如果可以仍希望大家可以幫手分享，萬分感激<br />\n<br />\n如有消息請致電 或直接whatsapp，因為未必會追到post. Thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後祝大家冬至快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聯絡人：<br />\n☎️63917338 朱生 (女婿)<br />\n<a href=\"https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=85263917338\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.whatsapp.com%2Fsend%3Fphone%3D85263917338&d=pK2oF7PWZi%2FXTPe7b0RN5kbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=552cb1fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=85263917338</a><br />\n<br />\n☎️93061962 林小姐 (女兒)<br />\n<a href=\"https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=85293061962\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.whatsapp.com%2Fsend%3Fphone%3D85293061962&d=pK2oF7PWZi%2FXTPe7b0RN5kbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=dc488abb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=85293061962</a><br />\n<br />\n☎️90208680 林太 (太太)<br />\n<a href=\"https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=85290208680\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.whatsapp.com%2Fsend%3Fphone%3D85290208680&d=pK2oF7PWZi%2FXTPe7b0RN5kbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=98ae32ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=85290208680</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5twR1d3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5twR1d3.png&h=80e7e1a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6aX9NT8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6aX9NT8.png&h=38e786d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n失蹤前衣著<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vtBuNUa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvtBuNUa.png&h=b71916f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n報案編號"},{"pid":"271612c2f8ca68ea0d7639f540eb6ac78d072ab6","tid":951002,"uid":116561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:36:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812b10d27e59d7e5298f791f2db1117b14b30534","tid":951002,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:36:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"af45f28f5fe440d6022bd84b972313dc7cf82947","tid":951002,"uid":158149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:36:23.000Z","msg":"push 冬至快樂"},{"pid":"c509c8e0de5f1664af1b21dd6d4494f9738109f4","tid":951002,"uid":116561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:36:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72ac1386af1a4d468fad56e3a77869bb49bd22e","tid":951002,"uid":116561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:38:43.00